1. *Kad* sam bio mali, obožavao sam da se igram. (When I was a kid, I used to love playing.)

2. Uvek mi je potrebno da čekam *kad* se gdešam. (I always need to wait when I travel.)

3. Trčao sam koliko sam mogao, ali *kad* sam stigao, napravio sam grešku. (I ran as much as I could, but when I arrived, I made a mistake.)

4. *Kad* god želim da odmorim, odem u šetnju. (Whenever I want to rest, I go for a walk.)

5. Uvek ćeš znati *kad* je vreme za pauzu. (You will always know when it's time for a break.)